info_en: Waterdrop are the native asset of the Rainbow network. Native means that lumens are built into the network. Asset is how the network refers to an item of value that is stored on the ledger. One lumen is a unit of digital currency, like a bitcoin. While you cant hold a waterdorp in your hand, they are essential to the Rainbow networkthey contribute to the ability to move money around the world and to conduct transactions between different currencies quickly and securely.
